{"tid":1123913,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[MARVEL撚入]10年，咁就過去喇，真係好撚感動","createTime":"2019-04-24T17:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T11:46:04.000Z","uid":249040,"like":7,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7fc4c33473e3073e98ca1aae2958ad87819b36b6","tid":1123913,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:52:46.000Z","msg":"第一套MCU 電影IM果陣我只係得5歲<br />\n斬眼間十年就過去，睇住各個角色年華漸老，陪伴左自己整整十年，由小學到幼稚園到今年揀科<br />\n今日睇完END GAME，覺得所有野都已經回不去，十年時間既光陰，一下子就突然落幕<br />\n今日特登請左病假，唔係因為我要睇復聯4，而係我知道我睇完復聯4個心一定會羅羅亂<br />\n好似同初戀女朋友分手咁，嗯，再也不能愛上別個的感覺，就是這樣了<br />\n即使之後再有更深度既英雄片，更加出色既電影宇宙<br />\n可能因為呢十年，我已經成長，呢段青春已經返唔到轉頭了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a7509a99810a0b2c4f5f03518e8761e05b288b4","tid":1123913,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T18:00:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9de540260ac4b64d87b13fcdfe9d54a3003e863f","tid":1123913,"uid":171273,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T19:24:28.000Z","msg":"15歲<br />\n兒登<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36dd9aa1c4e80494026527f1620e788270b2b16d","tid":1123913,"uid":47041,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T19:35:05.000Z","msg":"十年前老豆仲未射我出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b16148df6b975ccfe54161ba2ea4df2443ec2b","tid":1123913,"uid":247060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T20:03:57.000Z","msg":"早啲瞓 夠鐘翻學"},{"pid":"1c4e3540e9ced58d425cfd52629c58cb3b3c9d04","tid":1123913,"uid":61450,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T21:53:46.000Z","msg":"嘩屌你老母 初戀女朋友嗰句真係睇到起撚曬雞皮 <br />\n揀好科未呀"},{"pid":"80971e0e0f3882ff2ad433ca823ce3e52056b191","tid":1123913,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T23:53:00.000Z","msg":"小學到幼稚園<img src=\"/ass